## multiply variable

Multiplies first argument and second argument.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
multiply: {
    (a: number, b: number): number;
    (a: number): (b: number) => number;
    (a: bigint, b: bigint): bigint;
    (a: bigint): (b: bigint) => bigint;
}
```

## Example 1


```ts
// Basic
multiply(2, 3) // 6

```

## Example 2


```ts
// Bigint
multiply(2n, 3n) // 6n

```

## Example 3


```ts
// Curry
const double = multiply(2)
double(4) // 8

```
